    <h2>Effective Use of HTML5</h2>

    <p>This document demonstrates the use of several HTML5 features, including lists, tables, media embedding, and a structured, validated form. All elements are built using only HTML5, without any CSS or JavaScript.</p>

    ---

    <h3>Lists and Tables</h3>

    <p>Lists and tables are excellent tools for organizing information. <strong>Unordered lists</strong> (<code>&lt;ul&gt;</code>) are perfect for items where the order doesn't matter, while <strong>ordered lists</strong> (<code>&lt;ol&gt;</code>) are used when sequence is important. Tables (<code>&lt;table&gt;</code>) are ideal for displaying tabular data.</p>

    <h4>Ordered List of Planets:</h4>
    <ol>
      <li>Mercury</li>
      <li>Venus</li>
      <li>Earth</li>
      <li>Mars</li>
      <li>Jupiter</li>
    </ol>

    <h4>Unordered List of Star Systems:</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Alpha Centauri</li>
      <li>Sirius</li>
      <li>Proxima Centauri</li>
      <li>Vega</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Simple Table for Planet Data:</h4>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Planet</th>
          <th>Diameter (km)</th>
          <th>Number of Moons</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Earth</td>
          <td>12,742</td>
          <td>1</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Mars</td>
          <td>6,779</td>
          <td>2</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Jupiter</td>
          <td>139,820</td>
          <td>95</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    ---

    <h3>Embedding Media Content</h3>

    <p>HTML5 provides semantic tags for embedding different types of media. The <code>&lt;video&gt;</code> tag is used for video, <code>&lt;audio&gt;</code> for audio, and <code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code> for external content like a map. The <code>controls</code> attribute adds playback controls, while <code>poster</code> specifies an image to display before the video starts.</p>
    <br>

    <h4>Video Example:</h4>
    <video width="320" height="240" controls poster="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/S-d4G-2E0fM/maxresdefault.jpg">
      <source src="https://www.w3schools.com/html/mov_bbb.mp4" type="video/mp4">
      Your browser does not support the video tag.
    </video>
    <br>
    <br>

    <h4>Audio Example:</h4>
    <audio controls>
      <source src="https://www.w3schools.com/html/horse.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
      Your browser does not support the audio element.
    </audio>
    <br>
    <br>

    <h4>Iframe Example (Google Maps):</h4>
    <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3022.25367675276!2d-73.9878201845946!3d40.7484400793282!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x89c2596c567a126d%3A0x7a3a96b3a3d2e2d5!2sEmpire%20State%20Building!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1628173499427!5m2!1sen!2sus" width="600" height="450" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy"></iframe>

